Icarus worked exclusively in [[Realmspace]]. On top of his command of the ''Arrow of Justice'', he also commanded an elven [[Spelljammer|spelljamming]] fleet consisting of the following vessels:
* 7 [[Armada (spelljammer)|armadas]];
* 1 [[monarch armada]];
* 50 [[flitter]]s;
* 12 [[Man-o-war|men-o-war]];
* 1 [[radiant ship]];
* 5 [[eel ship]]s.
